WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.470
Good morning, family. How are y'all doing

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:05.309
today? Well, praise the Lord! I'm excited

00:00:05.319 --> 00:00:07.389
to be here today. I have some things

00:00:07.399 --> 00:00:10.110
on my heart we're going to pray about.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:12.350
You know, a lot of people—I guess I

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:15.150
caused some confusion on not the last

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:17.189
video, but the video

00:00:17.189 --> 00:00:17.199
before—people

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:19.029
are asking, "What are you talking about,

00:00:19.039 --> 00:00:20.470
the economy? I thought it was going to

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:23.230
crash and all this stuff."I saw when

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:27.150
President Trump wins the election, the

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:30.950
economy and the news of

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:34.069
winning causes a ripple throughout the

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:36.750
whole world. There are a

00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:38.630
lot of people that will be excited; yes,

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:39.750
there will be a lot of people that are

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:43.190
not excited. But for the most part, what I

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:46.869
was shown was that there is an

00:00:46.869 --> 00:00:46.879
economic—like

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:48.950
people, when they hear the news,

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:50.750
the stock market rallies and gets

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:52.869
excited and things happen. I saw a

00:00:52.879 --> 00:00:55.590
pumping of the economy. And so people

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:57.150
were like, "I thought you said you saw the

00:00:57.160 --> 00:01:00.389
economy crash?"I did, and I still do. I

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:02.630
told you all that it was like a house of

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:05.990
cards. I saw the BRICS nations

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:08.030
rising up and trying to create

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:11.910
their digital platform. I said, "I believe

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:13.990
this is me looking into a

00:01:13.990 --> 00:01:14.000
vision."Whenever

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.910
I've said this, there

00:01:16.910 --> 00:01:16.920
is depth

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:19.109
perception in a

00:01:19.119 --> 00:01:21.990
vision where you are looking, whether it's a

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:25.990
year, a month, or two years or

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.030
whatever; it's very hard to tell. You have

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.910
to... it's like this: the Lord told me,

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:34.510
"You are going to have to be so

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:36.429
precise. It's going to be like a ticking

00:01:36.439 --> 00:01:39.590
of a clock when it comes to

00:01:39.590 --> 00:01:39.600
investments."He

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:42.510
said

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:43.910
because if you're too early, you're too

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.310
early; if you're too late, you're too late.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.429
You have to be just like a clock. He was

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:50.429
referring in my heart because my favorite

00:01:50.439 --> 00:01:52.230
watch is a Rolex. I've never owned one,

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:54.910
but I think they're beautiful. And

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:58.870
he talked to me about how

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:03.069
precise a tick is: tick, tick, tick, tick, tick.

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:06.029
Invest. Tick, tick, tick. Don't invest. If

00:02:06.039 --> 00:02:09.550
you do it by the

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:12.190
precision of the heartbeat of the Father,

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.790
you will not miss it. But if you're doing

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:17.030
it too early, it is too

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:20.070
early in investments. If you get in there

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:22.830
and you invest too early and he's

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:24.550
not saying that yet, and you put

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.830
something into something,

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:29.350
then you could

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:30.390
lose money,

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:34.150
right? Or it could be way

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:35.830
too early or whatever.

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.229
And then all of a sudden he says,

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:40.350
"Invest in this,"and you are scared to

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.990
invest in it because your

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:44.190
flesh is involved. And he's saying, "Do

00:02:44.190 --> 00:02:44.200
something,"and

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:45.710
you're going, "Man, I don't

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:45.720
know."And

00:02:45.720 --> 00:02:47.990
then it shoots up really high

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.030
and you miss the opportunity to put your

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.670
money in it. And so that's why I'm saying

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:55.869
it has to be you, when you are doing

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:57.550
stuff with

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:00.869
money, hearing his voice right on

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:03.229
every single thing. So whenever I tell

00:03:03.239 --> 00:03:06.630
you the Lord is telling me a season of

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:09.589
grace, a time of grace, he said, "Brandon,

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:11.630
there has been much prayer that has

00:03:11.630 --> 00:03:11.640
gone

00:03:11.640 --> 00:03:15.030
before me over the month of October,

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:18.430
and I am granting more grace

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:22.270
over what I would see was

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:25.949
going to be hell on earth."There was

00:03:25.959 --> 00:03:28.830
like a small

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:31.350
little window. Now, what that

00:03:31.350 --> 00:03:31.360
entails—if

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:33.270
that's until the first of the year, a

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.470
small window—I have no idea. Ladies and

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.589
gentlemen, I'm human, and when I'm

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:39.190
praying, I'm just telling you

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:42.110
exactly what I'm seeing. And so I want

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:44.830
you to pray about it too. It's not for

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:47.630
you to ride on the back and

00:03:47.640 --> 00:03:49.350
just go, "Hey, you figure it out,

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:52.270
Brother Brandon."No, no, no. You help me. If

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:54.670
I bring something to you to pray about

00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:56.630
and it doesn't witness with you, then say,

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:58.670
"That doesn't sound like anything.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:01.190
That doesn't witness with my spirit at all.

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:02.589
I don't believe you're hearing

00:04:02.589 --> 00:04:02.599
the Lord."That's

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:05.270
fine. We

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:07.630
hear in part and we see in part. And so

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:09.910
what I may see, you may not see. You know,

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:11.550
a lot of people were like, "What did you

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:14.270
pray about the New York

00:04:14.280 --> 00:04:17.189
Yankees and all that for so

00:04:17.189 --> 00:04:17.199
long?"I

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:19.189
brought it up because the Lord

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:21.550
brought it up to me. I saw the vision of

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:23.749
the New York Yankees going to the World

00:04:23.759 --> 00:04:27.189
Series and the Los Angeles Dodgers clear

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:32.110
back in like May. And I saw

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:35.749
attempted attacks on Yankee Stadium,

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:38.629
and he kept telling me, "Watch the Yankees.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:40.550
Watch the Yankees."That's the only word

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:43.670
he was giving me: "Watch and pray for the

00:04:43.670 --> 00:04:43.680
Yankees."And

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:46.749
so when you add to or

00:04:46.759 --> 00:04:48.670
take away from anything whenever

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.870
he's talking to you... I'm just giving you

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.070
what I'm learning.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:55.310
I'm thinking in my

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:57.230
natural mind, even

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:59.830
into August, and he says, "Pay

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:01.950
attention to the Yankees."I'm thinking,

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:03.550
"Wow, the Yankees are going to go to the

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:06.150
World Series and win it."But he said it

00:05:06.150 --> 00:05:06.160
would

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.029
be the Los Angeles Dodgers and the

00:05:08.039 --> 00:05:11.830
Yankees. So just like he said, it happened.

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:13.790
So I'm at

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:17.790
October, and I told the pastor, "Hey, I

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.070
believe the Yankees are going to

00:05:19.070 --> 00:05:19.080
win,"because

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:20.710
we

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:24.070
just talk sports. And so I'm seeing

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:25.309
this at the prayer conference.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:26.950
Whenever I'm talking about this to

00:05:26.950 --> 00:05:26.960
the

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:29.990
pastor, I'm going, "Well, you

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.870
know, the Lord's been

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:33.710
telling me to watch the Yankees

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:36.029
since May."I mean, this is a long

00:05:36.029 --> 00:05:36.039
time—that

00:05:36.039 --> 00:05:38.270
we pray

00:05:38.280 --> 00:05:39.550
over it, that there would be no attacks

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:40.710
at the World Series, because I knew they

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:42.390
were going to the World Series. I just

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:45.070
had no idea if they were going to win. I

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:47.590
saw them going, but then I saw Los

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:49.590
Angeles. So when it got to the Friday

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:52.710
when they started the game, the Lord says,

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:55.110
"Los Angeles will win it in game five, the

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:56.309
whole

00:05:56.309 --> 00:05:56.319
thing."And

00:05:56.319 --> 00:05:59.350
I thought, "Game five, the whole

00:05:59.350 --> 00:05:59.360
thing?"But

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:02.790
they'll have three games

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:05.270
to pray over at Yankee Stadium

00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:09.589
that nothing happens. And that was,

00:06:09.599 --> 00:06:12.110
I believe, Monday,

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:14.189
Tuesday, Wednesday.

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.550
Three games in a row at Yankee

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:21.350
Stadium, but they would lose in game five.

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:24.270
And I was like, "Oh,

00:06:24.270 --> 00:06:24.280
wow."Lord,

00:06:24.280 --> 00:06:25.670
I thought they were going to win. Not

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:27.950
that it matters,

00:06:27.960 --> 00:06:30.390
but it's learning

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:34.629
to listen to his voice.

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:38.990
Do not assume

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:43.350
anything. Do not think for him,

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.830
thinking, "Well, I believe this is what

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:48.870
you're saying."Don't add to it. He said,

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:50.870
"Pray for the Yankees. Pray for the

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:53.110
stadium. Pray for this."And here I am, you

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:56.189
start adding to the prophetic word by

00:06:56.199 --> 00:06:59.110
saying, "Oh, the Yankees are going to

00:06:59.110 --> 00:06:59.120
win."But

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:01.029
when it got down

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:05.270
to teaching me...

00:07:05.280 --> 00:07:06.830
I'm just letting you all in on something

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:08.950
that I never let a lot of people in on,

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:10.869
and I'm obviously going to let thousands

00:07:10.879 --> 00:07:14.189
in now. But this is how I learn, and

00:07:14.199 --> 00:07:16.790
this is how he teaches me to flow in my

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:20.350
gift and how I see and hear.

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:22.589
Because I'm a work in progress and

00:07:22.599 --> 00:07:24.990
I'm hearing things, this is how I do it.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.830
And so whenever the Lord is

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:29.550
instructing me, you get pieces of

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:31.629
the puzzle and you

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:34.830
build yourself. You do

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:37.629
not become a champion in anything

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:40.110
without practice. I don't care who you

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:42.070
are. If you think that you're just going

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:44.270
to jump right out and be a LeBron James

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:47.790
or a Michael Jordan in anything you do,

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.510
it's impossible. You have to

00:07:50.520 --> 00:07:53.469
learn how to... when you're

00:07:53.479 --> 00:07:55.390
riding a bike, you learn just as much how

00:07:55.400 --> 00:07:57.589
to pick yourself up when you fall than

00:07:57.599 --> 00:08:01.149
you do whenever you are

00:08:01.149 --> 00:08:01.159
an

00:08:01.159 --> 00:08:06.230
amazing BMX biker, or a Joe Montana, or Troy

00:08:06.230 --> 00:08:06.240
Aikman,

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:09.230
or Emmitt Smith, or

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:11.309
somebody in sports that was the best

00:08:11.319 --> 00:08:14.029
at their level. You

00:08:14.039 --> 00:08:17.670
do not become a great until you practice

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:20.670
in high school all

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:22.390
the way up to college, and then you keep

00:08:22.400 --> 00:08:25.230
going. You do not become a great

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:29.110
overnight, basically, in anything.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.469
And even

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:35.389
listening to the voice of the Lord, you

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:38.750
practice his presence. You practice, and

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:41.709
when you fall, you pick yourself back up.

00:08:41.719 --> 00:08:44.310
You keep going and you go, "Well, man, I

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:46.509
missed it

00:08:46.509 --> 00:08:46.519
big,"whatever.

00:08:46.519 --> 00:08:48.509
I'm trying to

00:08:48.519 --> 00:08:50.790
paint a picture for you all. So

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:52.509
here, I

00:08:52.509 --> 00:08:52.519
saw

00:08:52.519 --> 00:08:55.190
about the Yankees. So I'm

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.550
assuming privately between my wife and I

00:08:57.560 --> 00:09:00.630
and my kids and my pastor

00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:04.069
that the Yankees were going to win.

00:09:04.079 --> 00:09:05.310
And this is just something that we just

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:07.069
talked about privately. I never made it

00:09:07.079 --> 00:09:09.790
public. I just talked about this

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.150
because I thought, "Man, the Yankees are

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.630
going to win. This is

00:09:12.630 --> 00:09:12.640
cool."And

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:14.670
we'll watch it play out. So when

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:17.350
it got down to that Friday

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:19.069
when the World Series started, the

00:09:19.079 --> 00:09:21.230
Lord came to me and he said, "Brandon, Los

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:24.829
Angeles will win it in game

00:09:24.829 --> 00:09:24.839
five."And

00:09:24.839 --> 00:09:27.350
I said, "Wow."I said, "The Yankees are

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.470
only going to win one

00:09:28.470 --> 00:09:28.480
game?"So

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.190
you just talk over

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:32.670
things with the Lord. I just make a

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:35.430
note of it. I tell my son. We archive

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:38.030
it so we know, because this is

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:41.630
me learning. And so it gets down to game

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:45.430
five and the Yankees are up by like

00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:47.269
six points or whatever it was. It was a

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:50.190
lot. And I thought, "Man, I've missed

00:09:50.190 --> 00:09:50.200
it."And

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:53.910
then all of a sudden,

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:56.550
in the fifth inning, they started falling

00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:59.829
apart. And they blew a

00:09:59.839 --> 00:10:03.550
humongous lead with errors and

00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:05.470
dropping the ball and throwing the ball.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:08.230
It was just stupid plays. And they

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:11.389
lost the lead in the fifth

00:10:11.399 --> 00:10:15.430
inning in game five. And so for

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:17.550
you that don't care about sports, I'm

00:10:17.560 --> 00:10:19.030
just trying

00:10:19.030 --> 00:10:19.040
to...

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:20.470
for people who want

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:22.509
to learn.

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:27.750
So it got down to game

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:30.150
five and they blew the lead,

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:33.030
and they

00:10:33.030 --> 00:10:33.040
lost

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:35.790
the game. And it was just like the

00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:37.910
Lord said. But at the point whenever I'm

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:39.710
looking into it in the

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:41.310
natural, I'm thinking, "Man, I missed it.

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:42.829
There's going to be a game

00:10:42.829 --> 00:10:42.839
six."And

00:10:42.839 --> 00:10:44.829
I told my wife, "Surely I didn't

00:10:44.839 --> 00:10:47.350
miss both what the

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:50.550
Lord said about the fifth game and

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:52.310
who was going to win."Because I

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.790
assumed it was going to be the Yankees,

00:10:53.800 --> 00:10:56.310
like I said. And lo and behold, it

00:10:56.320 --> 00:10:58.069
happened just like the Lord said. And

00:10:58.079 --> 00:10:59.910
then he scolded me

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:03.069
and he said, "Brandon, you can never think

00:11:03.079 --> 00:11:05.949
for me that this is what you're assuming

00:11:05.959 --> 00:11:07.670
that I'm

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:11.110
saying. Never add to a word that I'm

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:13.910
giving you."This was a good example of

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:15.629
what I'm trying to practice with you,

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:18.590
trying for you to learn that whenever

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.949
you are looking into a vision, you do not

00:11:20.959 --> 00:11:23.710
add to or take away from anything. He said,

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:26.110
"Pray for the Yankees in the

00:11:26.110 --> 00:11:26.120
stadium."It's

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.949
exactly what he said. And he

00:11:28.959 --> 00:11:31.590
said, "I told you Los

00:11:31.590 --> 00:11:31.600
Angeles."He

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.590
said, "I never told you anything

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:37.069
else about who would win."I said, "You're

00:11:37.069 --> 00:11:37.079
right."I

00:11:37.079 --> 00:11:38.670
